<h2>Adapting means you save a life</h2>
<ul>
<li>Too often, shelters euthanize animals due to room constraints, but if more people adopted pets instead of buying them, the number of pets euthanized would lower dramatically.</li>
<li>When you adopt, not only do you save your loving new companion, but you make space for other animals who desperately need it, creating a domino effect of goodness.</li>
</ul>
